- `--slds-g-color-border-disabled-1`: Subtle border for disabled
- `--slds-g-color-border-disabled-2`: Stronger border for disabled

## Typography

### Font Size
- Scaled sizes based on `--slds-g-font-size-base`
- `--slds-g-font-scale-neg-2` through `--slds-g-font-scale-neg-1` (or as defined)
- `--slds-g-font-size-base`: Applicationâ€™s base font size
- `--slds-g-font-scale-1` through `--slds-g-font-scale-8` (or as defined)

### Font Weight
- Define text emphasis
- `--slds-g-font-weight-1` through `--slds-g-font-weight-7` (e.g., light to bold)
- `--slds-g-font-weight-4`: Normal weight

### Line Height
- Unitless multiplier of font-size
- `--slds-g-line-height-1` through `--slds-g-line-height-6`

## Spacing & Sizing

### Spacing
- Layout spacing like margin and padding
- `--slds-g-spacing-1` through `--slds-g-spacing-12`: Modular 4-based scale

### Sizing
- Height/width units relative to font-size or rems
- `--slds-g-sizing-1` through `--slds-g-sizing-12`

